cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and machine learning techniques for video object segmentation. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of GANs for unsupervised learning also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the use of depth information, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
